Privacy Policy
Last Updated: August 18, 2023
1. Introduction
Welcome to DeepArt, an AI-based art generation platform using DALLE-2. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and disclose your personal information when you use our app. By using DeepArt, you agree to the collection and use of your personal information as described in this Privacy Policy.
2. Information We Collect
We collect various types of information when you use our app, including:
DeviceID for account creation and login
Username (if provided by the user)
Profile picture (if uploaded by the user)
We use this information to provide and improve our services, personalize your experience, and ensure the security of our app.
3. How We Use Your Information
We may use your information for the following purposes:
Generating art based on user preferences
Customizing and improving our app
Communicating with you about our services
Analyzing usage patterns and trends
Enforcing our terms and policies
Preventing fraud and unauthorized access
We may also use your information in an aggregated and anonymized form for research and analytics purposes.
4. Sharing of Your Information
We may share your personal information with third parties in the following circumstances:
With your consent or at your direction
With our service providers who assist us in providing the app
In response to legal requests or to protect our rights
As otherwise required or permitted by law
We take reasonable steps to ensure that your personal information is handled securely and in accordance with this Privacy Policy.
5. Your Choices
You have certain choices regarding the personal information we collect and how it is used:
You can review and update your profile information at any time
You can manage your notification preferences
You can request deletion of your account and personal information
For more details on how to exercise these choices, please refer to our app settings or contact us using the information provided at the end of this policy.
6. Security
We take reasonable measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access and use. However, no security measure is completely foolproof, and we cannot guarantee the absolute security of your data.
7. Changes to this Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any material changes by posting the revised policy on our app or by other means. Please review this policy periodically for updates.
8. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about our Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
